Cell["Enter section title here", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"4489b3e0-8fbd-4978-ac26-44ee79f69a17"],

Cell["\<\
Enter subsection title here
start with the bohr model with the spherical harmonics to represent energy \
levels
1D, 2D and 3D particle in a box 
use these models to tell us about energy levels and electron position, hi \
light their correct prediction\[CloseCurlyQuote]s and their limitations\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9839804603282022`*^9, 
  3.983980620411549*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"eea02188-3164-4561-9dc4-\
e1ef5031dd86"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Enter subsubsection title here", "Subsubsection",ExpressionUUID->"90928e64-68ec-4e2d-9ccb-ec8428255f0a"],

Cell["\<\
1 part of the project could be playing around with different ways to plot and \
use this hydrogen wave function thing, change quantum numbers and plot it \
different ways to learn about quantum numbers and visualizations (Can this \
tell us about energy levels?)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9839804074698467`*^9, 
  3.9839804527377996`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f6ceaa38-aeac-4eb7-ad8a-\
9c762f79da89"],

